sentences: He is also the voice of Tigtone in the 2014 animated short, The Begun of Tigtone.
He also reprises his role as the titular character in a 2019 Adult Swim animated television series, Tigtone.
He holds a bachelor's degree in music from UC Berkeley, which he received in 1989.
